flowchart LR
    A[Private historical market data] --> B[Point-in-time feature builder]
    B --> C[Chronological WFO split]
    C --> D[Train side-specific models]
    D --> E[OOS candidate scoring]
    E --> F[Replay with costs + risk gates]
    F --> G[Window/month/side aggregate metrics]
    G --> H[Robustness comparison]
    H --> I[Select baseline or reject variant]
    I --> J[Paper/live parity smoke]
    J --> K[Runtime monitoring]

    A -. raw data not published .-> A
    D -. model binaries not published .-> D
    G --> P[Public aggregate CSVs]
